00:16:07.350 --> 00:16:08.510
It's on Android Wear.

00:16:08.510 --> 00:16:10.110
You can Cast to your TV.

00:16:10.110 --> 00:16:11.650
You can even use it in the car.

00:16:14.320 --> 00:16:16.090
Another great app is
WhatsApp messenger.

00:16:16.090 --> 00:16:18.010
It's great for messaging,
sending photos,

00:16:18.010 --> 00:16:20.200
group chat, and a lot more.

00:16:20.200 --> 00:16:23.110
And it's been available for
phones for a long while.

00:16:23.110 --> 00:16:26.330
And it's also available on
Android Wear and Android Auto.

00:16:26.330 --> 00:16:28.950
Do you see the pattern here?

00:16:28.950 --> 00:16:31.190
This is one of those
applications like music

00:16:31.190 --> 00:16:33.340
where you expect it
to work everywhere.

00:16:33.340 --> 00:16:35.357
And it does.

00:16:35.357 --> 00:16:37.440
You can keep the conversation
going whether you're

00:16:37.440 --> 00:16:40.410
waiting in line with your phone,
on a walk with your watch,

00:16:40.410 --> 00:16:42.150
or a quick road
trip with your car.

